    "description": {
      "zh": "塔斯马尼亚虎 (TT) 45+ 模块化背包系统可根据使用者的实际需要进行深度定制。背包顶盖可展开以扩充容量，在必要情况下也可整体卸除。还附带有绑带可携带笨重的武器设备，需要拿取时也相当方便。黑系复合迷彩版本。",
      "en": "The TT Modular Pack 45 is a system that can be customized to suit the user’s needs. The top flap can be raised to increase capacity or removed entirely if required. External straps allow attachment of bulky gear or equipment that needs to remain easily accessible. MultiCam Black version."
